Package pso


Interface Summary
Performance contract for ease of performance metric implementation
 

Class Summary
Candidate storage for position and performance information for particles of interest such as local bests or global best
PSOEngine Engine for Particle Swarm Optimisation a special kind of stochastic optimisation using particles exploring the state space implements contraction, ring or random topology see www.swarmintelligence.org for additional information
PsoParticle Particle for Particle Swarm Optimisation assumes float parameters see www.swarmintelligence.org for additional information
